					</ul>
				</section>

				<section class="legal-section">
					<h2>13. User-Submitted Content</h2>
					<p>
						If you submit feedback, suggestions, or other content to us (via contact forms or email), you grant
						Shemirat Enayim a perpetual, royalty-free license to use, modify, and incorporate that content into
						our resources. We will not share personally identifiable information without your consent.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section class="legal-section">
					<h2>14. Modifications to Terms</h2>
					<p>
						We reserve the right to modify these Terms of Service at any time. Changes will be effective immediately
						upon posting to this page. Your continued use of the Site after changes constitutes acceptance of the
						modified terms. The "Last Updated" date at the top of this page indicates when terms were last revised.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section class="legal-section">
					<h2>15. Modifications to Site</h2>
					<p>
