					<h2>16. Indemnification</h2>
					<p>
						You agree to indemnify and hold harmless Shemirat Enayim and its operators from any claims, damages,
						losses, or expenses (including legal fees) arising from your use of the Site or violation of these terms.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section class="legal-section">
					<h2>17. Governing Law</h2>
					<p>
						These Terms of Service shall be governed by and construed in accordance with applicable laws, without
						regard to conflict of law principles.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section class="legal-section">
					<h2>18. Severability</h2>
					<p>
						If any provision of these terms is found to be unenforceable or invalid, that provision shall be limited
						or eliminated to the minimum extent necessary, and the remaining provisions shall remain in full force.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section class="legal-section">
					<h2>19. Contact Information</h2>
					<p>
						For questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us at:
					</p>
					<p>
						<strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:contact@shemiratenayim.org">contact@shemiratenayim.org</a>
					</p>
				</section>

				<section class="legal-section acknowledgment">
					<h2>Acknowledgment</h2>
					<p>
						By using Shemirat Enayim, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by
						these Terms of Service.
					</p>
				</section>
			</article>
		</div>
	</main>

	<Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
	.legal-page {
		flex: 1;
		padding: var(--space-8) 0 var(--space-16);
		background-color: var(--color-gray-50);
	}

	.legal-content {
		max-width: 50rem;
		margin: 0 auto;
		background-color: white;
		padding: var(--space-10);
		border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
	}

	.legal-header {
		margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
		padding-bottom: var(--space-6);
		border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-gray-200);
	}

	.legal-header h1 {
		font-size: var(--text-4xl);
		font-weight: 800;
		color: var(--color-gray-900);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
	}

	.last-updated {
		font-size: var(--text-base);
		color: var(--color-gray-600);
		font-style: italic;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.legal-section {
		margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
	}

	.legal-section h2 {
		font-size: var(--text-2xl);
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--color-gray-900);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
	}

	.legal-section p {
		font-size: var(--text-base);
		line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
		color: var(--color-gray-700);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
	}

	.legal-section p:last-child {
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	.legal-section ul {
		margin: var(--space-4) 0;
		padding-left: var(--space-8);
	}

	.legal-section li {
		font-size: var(--text-base);
		line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
		color: var(--color-gray-700);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
	}

	.legal-section li:last-child {
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	.legal-section a {
		color: var(--color-primary-600);
		text-decoration: underline;
		font-weight: 500;
	}

	.legal-section a:hover {
		color: var(--color-primary-700);
	}

	.acknowledgment {
		background-color: var(--color-primary-50);
		padding: var(--space-6);
		border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
		border: 1px solid var(--color-primary-200);
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	.acknowledgment h2 {
		color: var(--color-primary-900);
		font-size: var(--text-xl);
		margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
	}

	.acknowledgment p {
		color: var(--color-primary-900);
		margin-bottom: 0;
		font-weight: 500;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.legal-content {
			padding: var(--space-6);
		}

		.legal-header h1 {
			font-size: var(--text-3xl);
		}

		.legal-section h2 {
			font-size: var(--text-xl);
		}
	}

	@media print {
		.legal-page {
			background-color: white;
		}

		.legal-content {
			box-shadow: none;
			padding: 0;
		}
	}
</style>
